<A>__{reaching the top, jennifer catches a glimpse of a familiar boy running into the front room. she slowly walks towards the open door we can't see inside the room from the hallway. but she pauses as she hears thud. thud. the same rhythmic thumping that karen heard. after a moment, jennifer steps inside the room, disappearing from our sight. we hear her suddenly draw a gasp. a beat. as we drift closer to the doorway, we notice something strange: the room appears to be growing darker. a sharp breathing can be heard from inside... quick, panicked gulps of air. growing faster. just as we reach the doorway, the harsh breathing stops. a moment of stillness. then the door is slammed shut from the inside.}
